# Aegis backend build context (Dockerfile.prod / Dockerfile.hotpatch)
# Dockerfile 只 COPY: pyproject.toml uv.lock README.md aegis/
# 其余一律排除，避免上下文膨胀 + 防止 .env 密钥进构建上下文

# --- 密钥 / 环境文件 (绝不进上下文) ---
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key

# --- VCS / IDE ---
.git
.gitignore
.github
.pre-commit-config.yaml
**/.git
.vscode
.idea

# --- Python 构建/缓存产物 ---
.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
.pytest_cache
.mypy_cache
.ruff_cache
.coverage
dist
build
*.egg-info

# --- 测试 (运行时镜像不需要) ---
aegis/tests

# --- 姊妹仓 / 前端 (各自独立构建，不进后端上下文) ---
aegis-console
aegis-agent
aegis-plugins
aegis-appstore
aegis-edge
aegis-watch
aegis-poc

# --- 文档 / 杂项 ---
docs
*.md
!README.md
*.log
**/*Zone.Identifier
